    ('cat_big_soft_ball_for_turn_taking', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for mixed pass games', 'INPODAK Pack of 4 Toddler Balls', 'INPODAK', 'Bigamart', 'https://bigamart.com/product/inpodak-pack-of-4-toddler-balls-with-pump-mini-basketball-mini-football-mini-playground-ball-mini-rugby-for-kids-toy-sports-ball-suitable-for-toddler-indoor-outdoor-play/', NULL, '£40.81', 'in_stock', '1-3 years', 'A pack of four soft five inch PVC toddler balls, with a football, basketball and playground ball sized for little hands to roll, catch and pass indoors or out.', 'Just past two and a half, shared play means sending the ball back and waiting a turn, not only chasing it alone. Four soft shapes keep short pass games going when one ball gets boring. Mixed pass games for living-room play without a hard sting if a catch is missed.', 'The variety of balls allows for different types of turn-taking games, from rolling the playground ball to gentle kicks with the football.', 'Requires inflation (pump included).', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://bigamart.com/product/inpodak-pack-of-4-toddler-balls-with-pump-mini-basketball-mini-football-mini-playground-ball-mini-rugby-for-kids-toy-sports-ball-suitable-for-toddler-indoor-outdoor-play/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_big_soft_ball_for_turn_taking', 2, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for rolling with you', 'Giant 45cm Mega Ball', 'Little Toy House', 'Little Toy House', 'https://littletoyhouse.co.uk/product/giant-45cm-mega-ball/', NULL, '£6.99', 'in_stock', '3+', 'An oversized soft fabric mega ball about 45cm across, light enough for a toddler to push and roll with you across carpet without the thump of a hard sports ball.', 'Big rolling needs two people once they want a proper back-and-forth job, not a solo kick into the sofa. A giant soft ball is easy to shove together and soft enough for indoor play. Rolling with you on tired evenings when cooperative play beats a chase around the room.', 'Its size requires two hands to manage, naturally promoting shared play and turn-taking when rolling it back and forth.', 'Supplied deflated; requires a pump.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://littletoyhouse.co.uk/product/giant-45cm-mega-ball/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_big_soft_ball_for_turn_taking', 3, 8, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for gentle kick passes', 'Soft Foam Football Size 3 Assortment', 'Smyths Toys', 'Smyths Toys', 'https://www.smythstoys.com/uk/en-gb/search/?q=soft+foam+football', NULL, '£4.99', 'in_stock', '3+', 'A size 3 soft foam football made for safe indoor and outdoor play, light enough to kick and pass without a hard sting if someone misses the catch.', 'Kick passes get clearer at this age: one rolls or kicks, the other waits, then sends it back. Soft foam keeps that practice kind on shins and living-room furniture. Gentle kick passes when you want shared turns with a familiar football shape, without a proper match ball in the house.', 'The size 3 is manageable for toddlers, and the soft foam makes it safe for shared kicking games.', 'Colours may vary.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.smythstoys.com/uk/en-gb/search/?q=soft+foam+football']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_big_soft_ball_for_turn_taking', 4, 14, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for oval ball passes', 'Soft Rugby Ball', 'Gompels', 'Gompels', 'https://www.gompels.co.uk/soft-rugby-ball.html', NULL, '£3.90', 'in_stock', 'Not specified', 'A soft 23cm rugby ball for indoor catch and pass practice, with an oval shape that rolls differently from a round playground ball and stays kind on little hands.', 'An oval shape makes passing a little trickier in a good way, once ordinary round rolls feel too easy. Soft fabric stays kind for indoor hand-offs while they work out the bounce. Oval ball passes for short shared games when a second soft ball adds a new puzzle without raising the risk.', 'The shape encourages two-handed catching and passing, which is great for cooperative play.', 'May be smaller than some ''giant'' balls, but good for grasping.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.gompels.co.uk/soft-rugby-ball.html']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_big_soft_ball_for_turn_taking', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for outdoor soft passes', 'FORZA Soft Foam PE Balls', 'FORZA', 'Net World Sports', 'https://www.networldsports.co.uk/forza-foam-pe-balls.html', NULL, '£15.00', 'in_stock', 'Not specified', 'Soft foam PE balls that do not sting on contact, with reduced bounce, sized for toddler hands and kinder outdoor pass and kick games than a hard playground ball.', 'Outdoor shared passes still need a soft ball once they want proper kicks on the grass. Reduced bounce keeps the game from racing off down the path. Outdoor soft passes for park or garden play when you want shared kicking without a stingy rebound every time.', 'The soft foam and reduced bounce make it easier for toddlers to successfully pass and receive the ball without it getting away from them.', 'Often sold in packs.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.networldsports.co.uk/forza-foam-pe-balls.html']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for first intentional marks', 'Crayola MyFirst Jumbo Crayons - Assorted Colours (Pack of 8)', 'Crayola', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/CRAYOLA-MyFirst-Coloring-Toddlers-Multicolored/dp/B00BUIE8OU', NULL, '£3.94', 'in_stock', '12+ Months', 'Easy-grip jumbo Crayola crayons in a pack of eight assorted colours, chunkier than standard sticks and built for little hands making early deliberate marks on paper.', 'Just past two and a half, drawing shifts from random scribbles toward lines and shapes they meant to make. Jumbo sticks cut the snap and frustration that thin crayons bring. First intentional marks with a familiar brand, when you want the next step after baby scribble sticks already in the house.', 'The jumbo size and easy grip are perfect for developing fine motor skills at 31-33 months, encouraging intentional scribbling and early shape-making, a clear stage shift from earlier fitting/matching activities.', 'Not explicitly washable, so supervision is recommended for younger toddlers prone to coloring off-paper.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/CRAYOLA-MyFirst-Coloring-Toddlers-Multicolored/dp/B00BUIE8OU', 'https://www.thebump.com/a/crayons-for-toddlers']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for wipeable wall marks', 'Crayola Ultra Clean Large Washable Crayons', 'Crayola', 'Mother & Baby (Amazon UK)', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Crayola-Ultra-Clean-Washable-Crayons/dp/B00K44458S', NULL, '£5.99', 'in_stock', '3+', 'Large Crayola Ultra Clean washable crayons that wipe from skin, clothes and painted walls more readily than ordinary wax sticks, still chunky enough for toddler hands.', 'Control is growing, yet stray marks still land on the wrong surface. Washable large crayons keep creative play going when you care about cleanup as much as colour. Wipeable wall marks for households that want confident drawing without treating every session like a decorating risk.', 'The washable feature directly addresses a common parental concern at this age, allowing toddlers to explore intentional mark-making freely without fear of permanent messes. The large size supports their developing grip for clearer turns and early shape-making.', 'May be slightly less vibrant than non-washable counterparts, but the convenience often outweighs this for parents.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned, especially for parents concerned about mess.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.motherandbaby.com/reviews/toddler-toys/crayons-for-toddlers/', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Crayola-Ultra-Clean-Washable-Crayons/dp/B00K44458S']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for steadier grips', 'Happy Triangles Jumbo Crayons 12 Pack', 'Happy Triangles', 'Hobbycraft', 'https://www.hobbycraft.co.uk/happy-triangles-jumbo-crayons-12-pack/6314011000.html', NULL, '£5.00', 'in_stock', 'Not specified, but ''jumbo'' and ''triangular'' suggest toddler-friendly', 'Triangular jumbo crayons in a twelve pack, shaped so little fingers settle into a steadier hold and less prone to rolling off the table during a scribble.', 'A steadier grip is part of the shift toward controlled drawing at this age. The triangle shape nudges fingers into place without a handwriting lesson. Steadier grips when they already like chunky crayons and you want the next bit of control without swapping to thin pencil sticks yet.', 'The triangular shape is key for encouraging a tripod grip, a significant developmental step at this age for more precise mark-making and early shape formation. This directly aligns with the ''My hands can make more now'' cluster.', 'May not be as widely available as Crayola, so check stock. Washability not specified.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned, particularly for encouraging proper grip.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.hobbycraft.co.uk/happy-triangles-jumbo-crayons-12-pack/6314011000.html', 'https://www.thebump.com/a/crayons-for-toddlers']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for big arm drawing', 'MÅLA Drawing paper roll, 30 m', 'IKEA', 'IKEA', 'https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/p/mala-drawing-paper-roll-70461088/', NULL, '£3.50', 'in_stock', 'Not specified, but suitable for children', 'A thirty metre IKEA MÅLA drawing paper roll that unrolls into a long floor or table strip, giving room for big arm movements and early shapes beyond small sheets.', 'Small pages can feel cramped once they want bigger sweeps and longer lines. A long roll turns the floor into a proper drawing run without rationing sheets. Big arm drawing for days when intentional marks need space, and you would rather not tape six A4 pages together again.', 'The large format directly supports the stage shift towards intentional mark-making and early shape-making by providing an unconstrained canvas. It allows for bigger, more confident movements than smaller paper, fostering a sense of control and purpose.', 'Requires a flat surface or easel for best use. Can be used with various art supplies.', 'buy', true, 'A practical and inspiring gift for any budding artist.', 'A good staple to have for creative play. Consider if the family already has a similar large paper option.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/p/mala-drawing-paper-roll-70461088/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for smooth beeswax colour', 'Honeysticks 100% Pure Beeswax Crayons (Jumbo)', 'Honeysticks', 'Mother & Baby (Amazon UK)', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Honeysticks-100-Pure-Beeswax-Crayons/dp/B01I2GNSWU', NULL, '£18.95', 'in_stock', '12+ Months', 'Jumbo Honeysticks beeswax crayons made from pure beeswax with a smooth, vivid laydown, sized for little hands and free from the usual paraffin wax mix.', 'Some children push harder and still want colour that shows first time. Smooth beeswax jumbo sticks reward that effort without a scratchy drag. Smooth beeswax colour when you prefer a natural wax option and they still mouth things now and then, with a chunky hold that matches this age.', 'The smooth glide and vibrant colors encourage confident and intentional mark-making, aligning with the stage shift. The natural, non-toxic material is a key benefit for this age group, where oral exploration is still common.', 'Higher price point than traditional wax crayons. Limited color palette in smaller packs.', 'buy', true, 'A high-quality, natural gift option for discerning parents.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Honeysticks-100-Pure-Beeswax-Crayons/dp/B01I2GNSWU', 'https://www.motherandbaby.com/reviews/toddler-toys/crayons-for-toddlers/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feeling_faces_and_story_books', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for sharing big worries', 'Ruby’s Worry: A Big Bright Feelings Book', 'Tom Percival', 'Waterstones UK', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/rubys-worry/tom-percival/tom-percival/9781408892152', NULL, '£6.99', 'in_stock', '3-7 years', 'A Big Bright Feelings picture book where Ruby’s worry grows and grows until she finds the courage to tell someone, told in warm pages for shared bedtime reading.', 'Just past two and a half, feelings start arriving as little stories they want to tell, not only faces to name. Ruby’s growing worry gives you a gentle plot to talk through their own version. Sharing big worries at bedtime without turning the evening into a feelings chart.', 'The narrative arc of Ruby''s worry growing and then shrinking when shared directly supports the ''telling my version'' objective, showing the power of verbalizing feelings and experiences. This is a significant step up from simply pointing to feeling faces.', 'None.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.waterstones.com/book/rubys-worry/tom-percival/tom-percival/9781408892152', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Rubys-Worry-Tom-Percival/dp/1408892154']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feeling_faces_and_story_books', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for angry roar nights', 'Ravi''s Roar: A Big Bright Feelings Book', 'Tom Percival', 'Waterstones UK', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/ravis-roar/tom-percival/tom-percival/9781408892183', NULL, '£7.99', 'in_stock', '3-5 years', 'A lively Big Bright Feelings picture book where Ravi turns into a tiger when he is angry, then finds his way back after the roar, in bright pages for short shared reads.', 'Anger can arrive as a whole body roar before words catch up. Ravi’s tiger story gives a shared picture for that rush and the softer return after. Angry roar nights get a kind story frame, so you can talk about their version without a behaviour chat on the sofa.', 'Ravi''s transformation into a tiger vividly portrays intense anger, offering a concrete way for children to understand and articulate their own feelings. The resolution, where Ravi learns to make amends, directly supports the ''telling my version'' stage by modeling how to process and communicate after a big emotional outburst.', 'None.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.waterstones.com/book/ravis-roar/tom-percival/tom-percival/9781408892183', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Ravis-Roar-Big-Bright-Feelings-Book/dp/1408892189']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feeling_faces_and_story_books', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for many feeling words', 'The Great Big Book of Feelings', 'Mary Hoffman, Ros Asquith', 'Waterstones UK', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/the-great-big-book-of-feelings/mary-hoffman/ros-asquith/9781847807588', NULL, '£9.99', 'in_stock', '4-9 years (BookTrust)', 'A large picture book that walks through lots of everyday feelings in different situations, with illustrations that invite pointing, naming and short chats as you turn the pages.', 'Once they can name happy and sad, the next step is a wider set of words for sticky evenings. This big feelings book spreads situations across pages so they can pick the one that matches their version. Many feeling words without pretending one emotion chart covers the whole day.', 'By presenting a wide array of feelings in different contexts, this book helps children build a richer vocabulary for their emotional experiences. This supports the ''telling my version'' stage by giving them more tools to articulate their internal states and connect them to external events, moving beyond basic happy/sad to more nuanced expressions.', 'Age range starts at 4 years on BookTrust, but content is suitable for advanced 31-33 month olds with adult guidance.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.waterstones.com/book/the-great-big-book-of-feelings/mary-hoffman/ros-asquith/9781847807588', 'https://www.booktrust.org.uk/book-recommendations/bookfinder/the-great-big-book-of-feelings/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feeling_faces_and_story_books', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for heart words chat', 'In My Heart: A Book of Feelings', 'Jo Witek, Christine Roussey', 'Waterstones UK', 'https://www.waterstones.com/book/in-my-heart/jo-witek/christine-roussey/9781419713101', NULL, '£13.99', 'in_stock', 'From 3 years', 'An interactive feelings picture book that links emotions like happiness, sadness, bravery and anger to vivid heart images, inviting your child to talk as you read together.', 'Telling their version needs a bridge between the feeling inside and words out loud. Heart images and short pages keep that chat concrete on tired evenings. Heart words chat when you want them in the conversation, not only listening to an adult explain how they should feel.', 'The book''s structure, with different feelings represented by unique illustrations and descriptions, provides a scaffold for children to articulate their own emotional experiences. This directly supports the ''telling my version'' stage by offering a framework for expressing complex internal states in a relatable way.', 'None.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.waterstones.com/book/in-my-heart/jo-witek/christine-roussey/9781419713101', 'https://www.reddit.com/r/UKParenting/comments/10qpd6t/best_books_about_feelings_for_toddler/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_feeling_faces_and_story_books', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for picnic worry talk', 'The Worrysaurus', 'Rachel Bright', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Worrysaurus-Rachel-Bright/dp/1408356139', NULL, '£7.99', 'in_stock', 'No specific age, but described as for young children.', 'A gentle picture book about a little dinosaur whose anxious thoughts try to spoil a picnic, until help and kind words bring him back to enjoying the day.', 'Worry often shows up as a busy head before a fun plan. The Worrysaurus gives a picnic sized story for that wobble and the soft way through it. Picnic worry talk for evenings when they need their version heard, without a heavy coping talk at bedtime.', 'This book provides a clear storyline where a character experiences and overcomes worry, offering a model for children to understand and articulate their own anxieties. The emphasis on parental support in managing feelings reinforces the ''telling my version'' objective by showing how communication can help alleviate big emotions.', 'None.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Worrysaurus-Rachel-Bright/dp/1408356139', 'https://www.scottishbooktrust.com/book-lists/picture-books-to-help-children-explore-emotions']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for hoop and toss kits', 'Jump-In Hoops & Bean Bags (part of The Researcher Play Kit)', 'Lovevery', 'Lovevery UK', 'https://lovevery.co.uk/products/the-play-kits-the-researcher', NULL, '£120.00', 'in_stock', '31-33 months', 'Jump in hoops and bean bags from Lovevery’s Researcher Play Kit, set up for hopping into rings, tossing to a target and short deliberate movement games indoors.', 'Just past two and a half, movement gets a job: jump here, toss there, wait a turn. Hoops plus bean bags give clear targets without inventing kit from cushions. Hoop and toss kits when you want deliberate balance and aiming play, and you are already in the Lovevery kit world or happy to borrow the idea.', 'The hoops and bean bags encourage deliberate aiming and jumping, directly supporting the ''balance and bravery'' cluster and the stage shift towards targeted movement at 31-33m.', 'Only available as part of ''The Researcher Play Kit'', not sold separately. Higher price point due to being part of a larger kit.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift if the family is already invested in the Lovevery system or values high-quality, age-specific play kits.', 'Check if the family already has a Lovevery subscription or similar high-quality gross motor play items.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://lovevery.co.uk/products/the-play-kits-the-researcher']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for coloured hoop targets', 'Plastic Hula Hoop Set (45.7cm)', 'Early Years Resources', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/plastic-hula-hoop-set/', NULL, '£12.60', 'in_stock', 'Early Years setting', 'A set of four durable plastic hula hoops at about 45cm, in different colours, for jumping into, stepping through and aiming bean bags indoors or in the garden.', 'Coloured rings turn open floor space into a simple course with rules they can follow. Smaller hoops are easier to step into and aim at than grown-up sized rings. Coloured hoop targets for indoor or garden bravery play when you want clear places to land, not random crashing around the room.', 'Supports the stage shift by providing a versatile tool for deliberate movement, aiming, and jumping, encouraging creative play with rules and targets.', 'No specific toddler age range, but ''Early Years setting'' implies suitability. No customer reviews available on the product page.', 'buy', true, 'A practical and fun gift that encourages physical activity and imaginative play.', 'A good basic set; consider upgrading only if a more specialized or durable set is needed.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/plastic-hula-hoop-set/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for aiming toss games', 'Play Bean Bags Pack Of 4', 'Early Years Resources', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/pe-sport/pe/bean-bags/', NULL, '£5.40', 'in_stock', 'Early Years setting', 'A pack of four colourful play bean bags sized for toddler throws, soft enough for indoor catch and aim games toward a hoop, spot or soft target.', 'Aiming is the new bit: not only flinging, but sending a soft bag toward a clear place. Four bean bags keep short shared toss games going without hunting tennis balls. Aiming toss games for balance and bravery play when you already have a hoop or floor spot ready as the target.', 'Directly supports the stage shift by providing a soft, safe object for deliberate throwing and aiming games, fostering coordination and control.', 'No specific toddler age range, but ''Early Years setting'' implies suitability. No customer reviews available on the product page.', 'buy', true, 'A simple yet effective gift that promotes active play and skill development.', 'These are a good basic set. Consider if a themed or more durable set is preferred.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/pe-sport/pe/bean-bags/']::text[], 'none'),
