    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for kit water experiments', 'Splashology!™ Water Lab', 'Learning Resources', 'Learning Resources UK', 'https://www.learningresources.co.uk/splashology-water-lab', NULL, '£27.95', 'in_stock', 'Ages 3+', 'A Splashology water lab kit with cups, tools and simple experiment pieces for pouring by hand, floating and watching how water moves between containers.', 'Just past two and a half, water play shifts toward trying something on purpose: pour, tip, compare, watch what happens. A kit with clear tools feeds that curiosity. Kit water experiments when they are ready for more than splash and dump, and you can borrow or try before a big outdoor table spend.', 'The Splashology! Water Lab directly addresses the stage shift by providing multiple tools for experimentation, fostering understanding of volume, buoyancy, and water flow, and encouraging cause-and-effect play. The included experiment cards guide purposeful exploration.', 'Contains small parts, requiring close adult supervision for children under 3 years old.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Use only with close adult supervision around water. CHOKING HAZARD! Small parts. Not for children under 3 yrs.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.learningresources.co.uk/splashology-water-lab']::text[], 'check_age_fit'),
